data.description: Check out this beauty on Chasse Ridge!! From curb appeal to the in ground pool and everything in between! This home offers a large formal dining, formal den/office and a huge living room w/ soaring ceilings, built in bookcases, and a beautiful GAS fireplace!!! The kitchen is equipped w/ custom cabinets, beautiful countertops and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom has an amazing on suite bath complete with double vanities, free standing soaker tub as well as a separate shower! Lets not forget the TWO walk in closets! Guest bedrooms are all spacious with great closet space as well. Additional amenities include; large game room w/ wet bar, full apartment above garage with living area/kitchen/bedroom/bath, oversized screened patio overlooking the huge sparkling pool/spa, resurfaced in 2022, w/ access to half bath! If lot size is a concern....check out the side entrance three car garage and spacious yard!!! This home is absolutely beautiful!!!! Call today for your personal tour!
